      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Peter McKenzie</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/webdu/page3\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9c/PeterMcKenzieWebDU2009.jpg/300px-PeterMcKenzieWebDU2009.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/9/9c/PeterMcKenzieWebDU2009.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PeterMcKenzieWebDU2009.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Peter McKenzie, WebDU 2009 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Peter McKenzie</b>,<br />\na New Zealand computer scientist, and software engineer at <a href=\"/index.php?title=Google&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Google (page does not exist)\">Google</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. As computer games programmer, Peter is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/LambChop\" title=\"LambChop\">LambChop</a> and <a href=\"/Warp\" title=\"Warp\">Warp</a>, and the <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> playing engine <i>Gonzo</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. His <a href=\"/Arimaa\" title=\"Arimaa\">Arimaa</a> bot <i>Jumbo</i> competed in the 2015 World Championship <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos_.26_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos &amp; Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos_.26_Games\">Photos &amp; Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_McKenzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos &amp; Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:McKenzieMatthias.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"McKenzieMatthias.jpg\" src=\"/images/d/dc/McKenzieMatthias.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/WCCC_1999\" title=\"WCCC 1999\">WCCC 1999</a>: <a href=\"/Heiner_Matthias\" title=\"Heiner Matthias\">Heiner Matthias</a> and <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter McKenzie</a>, <a href=\"/LambChop\" title=\"LambChop\">LambChop</a> -  <a href=\"/Zugzwang_(Program)\" title=\"Zugzwang (Program)\">Zugzwang</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"WCCC 1999\"]\n[Site \"Paderborn, Germany\"]\n[Date \"1999.06.19\"]\n[Round \"7\"]\n[White \"LambChop\"]\n[Black \"Zugzwang\"]\n[Result \"1/2-1/2\"]\n\n1.d4 d5 2.c4 dxc4 3.e3 Nf6 4.Bxc4 e6 5.Nf3 c5 6.O-O a6 7.dxc5 Qxd1 8.Rxd1 Bxc5 \n9.a3 b5 10.b4 Be7 11.Bd3 O-O 12.Bb2 Bb7 13.Nbd2 Nbd7 14.e4 Rac8 15.Rac1 Nb6 \n16.Bd4 Nfd7 17.Re1 Rfd8 18.Nb3 f6 19.Na5 Ba8 20.Be3 e5 21.Rc2 Kf7 22.Rec1 Rxc2 \n23.Rxc2 Rc8 24.Nd2 Bd8 25.Kf1 Ke7 26.Rxc8 Nxc8 27.Nab3 Bb6 28.Nc5 Bxc5 29.bxc5 \nNa7 30.Ke2 Nc6 31.Nb3 Nf8 32.Kd2 h6 33.Kc3 Ne6 34.g3 Nc7 35.f4 a5 36.f5 Kd7 \n37.Nd2 Nd8 38.a4 bxa4 39.Nc4 Nb5+ 40.Kc2 Kc7 41.Nxa5 Nc6 42.Bxb5 Nxa5 43.Bd3 \nBc6 44.Bc1 Nb3 45.Be3 Nd4+ 46.Kc3 Nf3 47.h4 Ne1 48.Bb1 Nf3 49.Kb4 Kc8 50.Kc4 \nKd8 51.Kd3 Nh2 52.Ba2 Ng4 53.Bg1 a3 54.Be6 h5 55.Ba2 Ke8 56.Bb3 Kd7 57.Bf7 Kc7 \n58.Bg8 Kd8 59.Be6 Bb7 60.Bf7 Kc7 61.Bb3 Ba8 62.Bc4 Bc6 63.Be6 Kd8 64.Bg8 Ke7 \n65.Bb3 Kd7 66.Bc4 Ke7 67.Ba2 Kd8 68.Bf7 Ke7 69.Bg8 Ba8 70.Bc4 Bb7 71.Bb3 Bc6 \n72.Bg8 Ba8 73.Ba2 Kd8 74.Bf7 Kc7 75.Be6 Bc6 76.Ba2 Kd8 77.Be6 Kc7 78.Bf7 Ba8 \n79.Be6 Kd8 80.Bc4 Ke7 1/2-1/2 \n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_McKenzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=20796\">Bratko-Kopec Test - Node Counts</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter McKenzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Bratko-Kopec_Test\" title=\"Bratko-Kopec Test\">Bratko-Kopec Test</a>, <a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">Node</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=131885\">Pawn endgame test suite</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter McKenzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 07, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Endgame\" title=\"Pawn Endgame\">Pawn Endgame</a>, <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=274926\">kiwipete perft position</a> by <a href=\"/Russell_Reagan\" title=\"Russell Reagan\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft_Results#kiwipete\" title=\"Perft Results\">Perft Results - kiwipete</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=284050\">Programmers: ETC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter McKenzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Enhanced_Transposition_Cutoff\" title=\"Enhanced Transposition Cutoff\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_McKenzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/102258763794961635717\">Peter McKenzie - Google+</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/peter-mckenzie-31397922/\">Peter McKenzie | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=44\">Peter McKenzie's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/db/operson.php?a=McKenzie%2C+Peter\">McKenzie, Peter</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/\">computer-go.info</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_McKenzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/webdu/page3\">photostream webDU 2009</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flickr\">Flickr</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/peter-mckenzie-31397922/\">Peter McKenzie | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/db/operson.php?a=McKenzie%2C+Peter\">McKenzie, Peter</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/\">computer-go.info</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arimaa.com/arimaa/wcc/2015/showGames.cgi\">2015 World Computer Championship</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/round.php?tournament=8&amp;round=7&amp;id=15\">Paderborn 1999 - Chess - Round 7 - Game 15 (ICGA Tournaments)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228180827\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 98/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 218/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template